snippet.description:
DJ/producer duo Sigma release their music video for their latest track “Find Me,” featuring powerful, heartfelt vocals by Grammy nominated Birdy who sold 10 million records with her platinum single “Skinny Love.” The video follows Stranger Things’ Millie Bobby Brown on an emotional journey through a busting city. “Find Me” was directed by Christopher Sims, who is best known for his work with stars like Usher, Ludacris, David Guetta, and more. 
"Find Me" is available now:
Spotify: http://po.st/FindMeSpotify
Apple Music: http://po.st/FindMeApple
iTunes: http://po.st/FindMeITunes
Follow Sigma:
https://twitter.com/sigmahq
https://www.facebook.com/sigma
https://soundcloud.com/sigmahq
https://www.instagram.com/sigma
http://www.sigmahq.com/
snippet.title: Sigma - Find Me ft. Birdy
